= Background
<background>
The integration of transformer architectures has revolutionized
sequential data modeling.

== Key Components
<key-components>
- #strong[Self-Attention:] Enables the model to weigh the significance
  of different words within the input sequence.

- #emph[Positional Encoding:] Injects crucial sequence order information
  directly into the input embeddings.

These components act in synergy to capture long-range dependencies
efficiently.
